Package civitas.celestis.math.natural

Interface NaturalVector

All Superinterfaces:
IntVector, Numeric, Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
MutableNaturalVector, NaturalVector2, NaturalVector3, NaturalVector4, RGBColor
public interface NaturalVector extends IntVector

A multidimensional natural number which has a direction and magnitude. This is essentially an IntVector with non-negative constraints enforced.

While mathematically incorrect, 0 is still allowed in natural vectors due to their importance in a variety of calculations.
